name: Sessão / #1 - O master chefe
description:
First piece of the “Sessão” collection.

When the session between friends catches fire, it doesn't take long for someone to take responsibility for the troop's munchies. #pizzalovers

*The collection entitled "Sessão" brings together six different illustrations previously produced, taking the troop of intergalactic friends to a classic session around Cogulândia, a magical and hallucinating world.
